         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[June 1855] ¶ My dear Mr Bateman. ¶  ¶ It will give me the greatest pleasure, to have the opportunity yet of meeting you; please, dear Sir, should the night not be to chilly for your going out, let me...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">55.06.00</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Edward La Trobe Bateman</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Private hands.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">[June 1855]<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition</seg>. M went to Sydney at the beginning of July 1855 before the North Australian Exploring Expedition, visiting Melbourne again briefly in January 1857 before returning to Sydney to pack up specimens to send to Kew.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Mr Bateman.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It will give me the greatest pleasure, to have the opportunity yet of meeting you; please, dear Sir, should the night not be to chilly for your going out, let me see you any time after seven at my place; if it is too cold I will call later on you.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">your very devoted friend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd Mueller.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also M to E. Bateman, June 1855 (second letter).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Mr Bateman.</p>
         </div>
